snippet.title: Drawing Mera - Aquaman - DC Comics - Amber Heard - Speed Drawing | Dawood Shahid Art
snippet.description:
Drawing "Mera" from the recent epic DC comics' movie release "AQUAMAN". She is a fictional character appearing in this movie and her special ability/power is that she can control Aqua/Water and remove water too from any space and surface when needed. As every other drawing, i enjoyed the whole process and  i tried to put as many effort and detailing as i could with patience of course into it. I hope you guys will like this epic artwork of mine. ✌️😊 #dccomics - #WBbros - #Aquaman - Aquaman - Time lapse video - Speed Drawing - #DawoodShahidArt 

Took me approximately 31 hrs, 4 mins and 23 secs of real time to draw this amazing piece of work.

◎ Dollar Pointer 0.3mm
